        <docTitle>Resolution adopted by the General Assembly on 26 May 2021</docTitle>
      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docProponent refersTo="#noMainCommittee">[without reference to a Main Committee (<inline name="originating document">A/75/L.87/Rev.1 and A/75/L.87/Rev.1/Add.1</inline>)]</docProponent>
